                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " A more realistic appraisal of the numerous",
                "factors entering into such measurement suggest the",
                "uncertainty of 10 to 20 percent."
              ]
